Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西弄起来还挺棘手的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.64,0:00:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为这样 才能成为优秀的傀儡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在想你到底打算宅多久
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来在制作新的傀儡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组装超复杂的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有宅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了备战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连木叶都变成了那样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后再发生什么也不足为奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 木叶是我们的盟国
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.14,0:00:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法置之度外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要重建彻底摧毁的村子可不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更重要的是填补空缺的火影之位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是组织上 还是精神上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为木叶支柱的火影如今不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.56,0:01:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了火影 他们能从晓带来的创伤中重振吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那里有他在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但对于村子而言 你不过是令人恐惧的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今你要离开我们 加入正规部队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.05,0:01:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会徒增痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上层都是一些丝毫不顾及你感受的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村民大都对你抱有恐惧心理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可只是空等的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更剧烈的痛苦将席卷而至
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有努力 靠自己解开这个枷锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不逃入只身一人的孤单之路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 终有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能像那家伙一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和砂隐的共同任务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种小事我们去不就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在砂隐和我们的边境引发的矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论委托哪一方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难免发生口角
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 就以同盟国的身份携手行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是最佳方案吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是能轻松一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是同盟国
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不过是木叶遇袭后结成的同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚开始不可能诸事顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为修复关系的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这次任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真睿智
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连这些事都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么 到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这辈子都不会理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是村子间 国家间的大人物们考虑的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不至于用这种语气来说嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然身为同盟国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家融洽相处才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 闲谈到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要赶往汇合地点了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 到底谁会最先抵达呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家比比看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 耍赖皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汇合地点应该就是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是来得太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然会迟到 肯定不是什么好人物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 一提到砂隐那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道是看不透他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是他们本来就很奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真心同木叶修好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不应该迟到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们迟到了 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我爱罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会和这家伙一起合作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 我爱罗 时间刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是来早了些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来的稍微晚了些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来没了杀气 变亲和了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂之…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对防御
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…痛…痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你到底打算干吗 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是打个招呼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扔个石头什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能伤到他嘛 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那两位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人竟然会使出绝对防御
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是何等恐怖的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来没那么容易被认同嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那帮家伙怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕过头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天京剧王子和铁扇公主没一起出动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勘九郎和手鞠才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在所属正规部队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的部下亚欧吉和克罗比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是亚欧吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是克罗比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这次任务的队长 旗木卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是鸣人 小樱和佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是些不成熟的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,综上所述
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗班从山的西侧出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们第七班则从东侧出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时进攻山顶的山贼据点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战开始时间为子时 行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说不用等那么久了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭我们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区山贼轻松就能搞定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是山贼 他们也是叛忍集团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且据说其中也有中忍级别的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别因为你 让我们几个都陷入危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明白作战方案了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事想事先打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我爱罗那家伙鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长们之间也会有需要商讨的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙竟然是队长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真臭屁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有跟踪者的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不出乱子最好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总得先跟你们打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你已经有谱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被村里的上层疏远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许会给你们添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶和砂隐一起完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加深感情 这才是任务的真正意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题越多羁绊也就越深了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 鸣人 小樱 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次可别迟到了 我爱罗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到他会自愿加入正规部队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们的任务也减轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上层们都相当高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 我们的酬劳也会提高了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂之我爱罗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的首级就归我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说我爱罗大人已经有所改变
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂之…绝对防御
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无数忍者命丧于此也是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一切顺利就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是山贼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是…我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上层都是一些丝毫不顾及你感受的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村民大都也对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经决定向前迈进了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能在这此停留
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底打算跟到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:11:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是写轮眼卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为气息隐藏得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不用顾忌继续前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不打算阻挠同盟国的忍者执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟国
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂隐的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将我们视为本次任务的监察者也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监察者…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是监视者啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗地观察任务的执行情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么监察
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是却戴着面具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人信不过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没被信任的恐怕是我爱罗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人的力量对于我们砂隐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 正因为是自家人才更具威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人的术 你们也见识过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你们不觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不应该存在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们打算除掉我爱罗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 对方还有暗杀部队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对木叶而言不见得是坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为其他村子的一个强大兵器将会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真过分 竟然将同村里的忍者给…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都能明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人对于两方村子来说都是威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不该存在于世的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是村子的危险道具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对他们而言 是要被抹杀的过去遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 我是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是不得不这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且我明白那就是最痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世界上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己就像不被需要的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我到底为何存在 为何而活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人绝不能活在这个世上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让他过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在砂隐 也该有能理解我爱罗的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们无法接受我爱罗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是不理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过可别把我们跟你们混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傀儡自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他本就是个毫不在意生命的杀人机器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个只会享受杀戮的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到这么容易就中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来 我们的任务就简单多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傀儡水遁.妖雨之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时…我爱罗大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是对我们这么说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们平安无事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们 怎么能抛弃同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我爱罗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂子吸收了凝聚查克拉的水 行动变得迟钝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结合也变弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的忍术已经被封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漩涡…鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终究只是影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真身只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不止一个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会再逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人是我们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扔下您逃走 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同我爱罗大人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然被这些废物给…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上层真是小看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要杀我 战斗力还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对付你们这就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽耍酷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是灾难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来我们这边的那帮人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本也被降服了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你们添麻烦了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,添麻烦的是这些家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也是砂隐的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 继续我们的任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要从这里开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这细微的羁绊之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想成为被他人需要的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是作为让人畏惧的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是作为砂隐的风影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把自己的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与村里的同伴们联系在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了众人的认可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实现了成为风影的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是从那家伙身上学来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过逐渐加深跟同伴的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以此找回了原来的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个村子有他的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比任何人都重视同伴以及同伴间的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是他和他所珍视的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次也一定能够挺过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还会变得更加成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说一次…能再说一次刚才你们说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扔下您逃跑 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这句
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是之前那句…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.86,0:22:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.31,0:22:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经浪费了这么多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没抓到小小的鸣人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.17,0:22:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:22:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过事态比预想得复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只凭我们医疗班 人手不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到之后的损失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.75,0:23:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须得不择手段吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.88,0:23:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 失控
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 绝对不会让你逃掉的
